org.usfirst.frc.team449.robot.generalInterfaces.poseCommand

Interface PoseCommand

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GetPathFromJetson, GoToPose, GoToPositionRelative

    public interface PoseCommand
    An interface for commands that take waypoints as an argument. These waypoints may change at runtime, so they need a method to update it.
